Package com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models

Class Flight

java.lang.Object
com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models.Flight
@Entity public class Flight extends Object
Represents a flight entity in the system. Contains details such as the flight number, departure and arrival times, airplane type, and associated seats and bookings.
